body_html:
@cpoptic I think the suggestion was to use the latest version of protobuf (3.6.0+) for TF v1.11

You probably need to try uninstall protobuf for every user account (root and non-root) to avoid your user setting picking a system installed protobuf.

Then you do the "pip install protobuf" again after making sure there are no protobuf system-wide.
